      "text": "あ、{user}さん。お疲れ様で～す",
      "startTime": 15.6463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。バレンタインイベント出演のために\nこころがリズノワの新曲を企画してるそうじゃないか",
      "startTime": 23.4130443573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですよ～\nアイデアが溢れ出過ぎて、困っちゃうくらいです！",
      "startTime": 28.879711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……自分の才能が恐ろしいです～",
      "startTime": 32.7463776906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。楽しみにしているからな\n無理だけはするなよ？",
      "startTime": 40.879711024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "は～い！",
      "startTime": 42.8130443573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_03_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワらしいバレンタインを全力でお見せしますよ～\n期待して待ってて下さいね～！",
